Selfies usually seem like an exercise in narcissism.

But today thousands of women shared striking shots of themselves at their most vulnerable, make-up free.

And
 joining the campaign, the mother of former Towie star Maria Fowler took
 it a step further - by baring her reconstructed breasts.

